# Pem: SerpAPI engines + app cards (reference)

**Implementation lives in** `backend/src/integrations/serpapi.service.ts` (`fetchJson` → `https://serpapi.com/search.json`) and **`backend/src/agents/agent-tools/prep-google-bundle.ts`** (intent-aware `Promise.all`). This file is the **engine directory** and **intent → card** map — not every engine is wired yet; add new engines beside existing methods and extend `executeGoogleBundle` / intent lanes.

## Base pattern

- Pass **`hl` / `gl`** when we add locale-aware engines (shopping bundle today uses SerpAPI defaults; extend `fetchJson` params as needed).
- **Parallelize** independent Serp + Tavily legs — see **`pem-core-loop.mdc`** and **`pem-search-provider-routing.mdc`**.

## Wired today

| Engine (SerpAPI) | Service method | `google()` vertical / intent |
|------------------|----------------|------------------------------|
| `google_shopping` | `googleShopping()` | `shopping` — SHOPPING; also RESEARCH/COMPARISON/DECISION + `shopping` |
| `amazon` | `amazonSearch()` | same bundle as above |
| `google_maps` | `googleMaps()` | `maps` — FIND_PLACE; LIFE_ADMIN+maps; RESEARCH family |
| `google` (organic) | `googleOrganic()` | `web` — FIND_PERSON, SCHEDULE, LIFE_ADMIN web; RESEARCH+`web` |
| `google` + `tbm=nws` | `googleNews()` | `news` — RESEARCH / COMPARISON / DECISION |
| `google_images` | `googleImages()` | `images` — RESEARCH / COMPARISON / DECISION |
| `google_jobs` | `googleJobs()` | `jobs` — RESEARCH / COMPARISON / DECISION |
| `google_finance` | `googleFinance()` | `finance` — RESEARCH / COMPARISON / DECISION |

**Types:** `GoogleVertical` in `backend/src/agents/agent-tools/prep-google-bundle.ts`. **`intentAllowsGoogleSerp`** includes `RESEARCH`, `COMPARISON`, `DECISION` so those intents get the **`google()`** tool.

## Product / buy behavior (SHOPPING)

- **`google(vertical: shopping)`** returns **`google_shopping`** + **`amazon_search`** + **`buying_guide_tavily`**. Cards must use **retailer PDP URLs** from those structured arrays — not news roundups (e.g. today.com). Forbidden hosts are stripped in **`backend/src/agents/schemas/shopping-product-url.ts`**.
- **App:** `SHOPPING_CARD` → **`PrepShoppingExperience`** (`app/components/sections/prep-detail-sections/PrepShoppingExperience.tsx`).

