## Expo / RN

- Prefer **`RemoteImageOrPlaceholder`** + **`normalizeRemoteImageUri`**; prefer **`serpapi_thumbnail`** when SerpAPI provides it (see **`pem-search-provider-routing.mdc`**).
- New card types: add a section component under `app/components/sections/prep-detail-sections/` and branch in **`PrepAdaptiveStack`** / `pemApi` icon mapping as today.

